          <h2>Looking for sustainability</h2>
          <p>In many different industries, sustainable practices in production can be marked by a stamp of seal indicating that it has gone through an eco-friendy process or evaluation, and these can be halpful in deciding which products to purchase when looking for a greener option.</p>
        
